data.description: This 3 bedroom plus loft/game room, 2.5 bath, 2 story home in Roseview is a must see! Living area flows into kitchen. Upstairs master is complete with full bath, dual vanity and walk in closet. Loft upstairs is a great space for kids play room or craft room! Two additional bedrooms and full bath located upstairs with half bath located downstairs. Close to schools and shopping. Backyard is work in progress, and it has great potential for more. Come and see it before it's gone!
